<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>istio on Aiden's Laboratory</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/tags/istio/</link><description>Recent content in istio on Aiden's Laboratory</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><copyright>Copyright © 2020-2021, Jongseob Jeon; all rights reserved.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/tags/istio/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>밑바닥부터 시작하는 Seldon-Core - 설치 [Istio Ver.]</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/from-scratch/install-istio/</link><pubDate>Fri, 14 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/from-scratch/install-istio/</guid><description>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>밑바닥부터 시작하는 Seldon-Core 순서&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>설치
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/from-scratch/install-istio/">밑바닥부터 시작하는 Seldon-Core - 설치 [Istio Ver.]&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/from-scratch/install-ambassador/">밑바닥부터 시작하는 Seldon-Core - 설치 [Ambassador Ver.]&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="pre-requisites">Pre-requisites&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Minikube&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Helm&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Ingress&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Istio&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h3 id="1-minikube">1. Minikube&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>사용한 minikube version은 다음과 같습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube version
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>minikube version: v1.20.0
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>commit: c61663e942ec43b20e8e70839dcca52e44cd85ae
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>minikube의 default config는 memory의 경우 2048mb 입니다. 이 경우 실습 중 메모리가 부족해서 OOM이슈가 생겨서 정삭적으로 진행할 수 없을 수 도 있습니다. OOM을 방지하기 위해서 minikube의 메모리를 4096mb로 늘려둡니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube config &lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> memory &lt;span class="m">4096&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>❗ These changes will take effect upon a minikube delete and &lt;span class="k">then&lt;/span> a minikube start
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>minikube를 실행시킵니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube start
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>😄 minikube v1.20.0 on Ubuntu 18.04
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>✨ Automatically selected the docker driver. Other choices: virtualbox, ssh
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>👍 Starting control plane node minikube in cluster minikube
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>🚜 Pulling base image ...
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>🔥 Creating docker container &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">CPUs&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>6, &lt;span class="nv">Memory&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>4096MB&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> ...
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>🐳 Preparing Kubernetes v1.20.2 on Docker 20.10.6 ...
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> ▪ Generating certificates and keys ...
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> ▪ Booting up control plane ...
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> ▪ Configuring RBAC rules ...
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>🔎 Verifying Kubernetes components...
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> ▪ Using image gcr.io/k8s-minikube/storage-provisioner:v5
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>🌟 Enabled addons: storage-provisioner, default-storageclass
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>🏄 Done! kubectl is now configured to use &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;minikube&amp;#34;&lt;/span> cluster and &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;default&amp;#34;&lt;/span> namespace by default
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="2-helm">2. Helm&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/">helm 공식 홈페이지&lt;/a>의 방법을 따라 합니다. 이 때 버전은 3 이상이어야 합니다.&lt;br>
여러 방법중 스크립트 방법을 이용해 설치하겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl -fsSL -o get_helm.sh &amp;lt;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/master/scripts/get-helm-3&amp;gt;
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>chmod &lt;span class="m">700&lt;/span> get_helm.sh
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>./get_helm.sh
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="3-ingress">3. Ingress&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>minikube에서 ingress addon 을 사용합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube addons &lt;span class="nb">enable&lt;/span> ingress
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span> ▪ Using image k8s.gcr.io/ingress-nginx/controller:v0.44.0
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span> ▪ Using image docker.io/jettech/kube-webhook-certgen:v1.5.1
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span> ▪ Using image docker.io/jettech/kube-webhook-certgen:v1.5.1
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>🔎 Verifying ingress addon...
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span>🌟 The &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;ingress&amp;#39;&lt;/span> addon is enabled
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="4-istio">4. Istio&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://istio.io/latest/docs/setup/getting-started/">Istio 공식홈페이지 가이드&lt;/a>를 따라합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="download-istio">Download Istio&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>스크립트를 이용해 다운로드합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl -L &amp;lt;https://istio.io/downloadIstio&amp;gt; &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> sh -
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> istio-1.9.5
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">PATH&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$PWD&lt;/span>/bin:&lt;span class="nv">$PATH&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="install-istio">Install Istio&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>istioctl을 이용해 설치합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; istioctl install --set &lt;span class="nv">profile&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>demo -y
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>✔ Istio core installed
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>✔ Istiod installed
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>✔ Egress gateways installed
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>✔ Ingress gateways installed
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span>✔ Installation &lt;span class="nb">complete&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>default namespace에 istio-injection을 시켜서 istio-system이 생성되게 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl label namespace default istio-injection&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>enabled
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>namespace/default labeled
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="ingress-ip-and-ports">ingress ip and ports&lt;/h4>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>ingress port 설정하기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">INGRESS_PORT&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>kubectl -n istio-system get service istio-ingressgateway -o &lt;span class="nv">jsonpath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{.spec.ports[?(@.name==&amp;#34;http2&amp;#34;)].nodePort}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">SECURE_INGRESS_PORT&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>kubectl -n istio-system get service istio-ingressgateway -o &lt;span class="nv">jsonpath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{.spec.ports[?(@.name==&amp;#34;https&amp;#34;)].nodePort}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>port 확인하기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; &lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$INGRESS_PORT&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">30687&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; &lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$SECURE_INGRESS_PORT&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">30520&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>Ingress ip 설정하기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">export&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">INGRESS_HOST&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">$(&lt;/span>minikube ip&lt;span class="k">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>ip 설정 확인하기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; &lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">$INGRESS_HOST&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>192.168.49.2
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="seldon-core">Seldon-core&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="install-seldon-core">Install seldon-core&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>namespace 생성&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl create namespace seldon-system
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>namespace/seldon-system created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>helm chart 생성&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>helm install seldon-core seldon-core-operator &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span> --repo &amp;lt;https://storage.googleapis.com/seldon-charts&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span> --set usageMetrics.enabled&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span> --namespace seldon-system &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span> --set istio.enabled&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>상태 확인&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get po -n seldon-system
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>seldon-controller-manager-559c567c9-pjtpl 1/1 Running &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="istio-setting">Istio setting&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>istio-ingress.yaml&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c">## istio-ingress.yaml&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">networking.istio.io/v1alpha3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Gateway&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">seldon-gateway&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">namespace&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">istio-system&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">selector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">istio&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">ingressgateway&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="c">## use istio default controller&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">servers&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">port&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">number&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="m">80&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">http&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">protocol&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">HTTP&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">hosts&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;*&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>다음과 같은 istio ingress 를 생성 후 apply 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k apply -f istio-ingress.yaml
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>gateway.networking.istio.io/seldon-gateway created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="sample-deploy">Sample deploy&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>namespace 생성&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl create namespace seldon
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>pod 생성&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>kubectl apply -f - &lt;span class="s">&amp;lt;&amp;lt; END
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">apiVersion: machinelearning.seldon.io/v1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">kind: SeldonDeployment
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">metadata:
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> name: iris-model
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> namespace: seldon
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">spec:
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> name: iris
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> predictors:
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> - graph:
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> implementation: SKLEARN_SERVER
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> modelUri: gs://seldon-models/sklearn/iris
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> name: classifier
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> name: default
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> replicas: 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">END&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>minikube tunnel&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; minikube tunnel
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>Status:
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span> machine: minikube
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span> pid: &lt;span class="m">117019&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span> route: 10.96.0.0/12 -&amp;gt; 192.168.49.2
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span> minikube: Running
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> services: &lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>istio-ingressgateway&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> errors:
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> minikube: no errors
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> router: no errors
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> loadbalancer emulator: no errors
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>ingress external ip 확인하기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; k get svc -n istio-system
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>istio-egressgateway ClusterIP 10.104.239.89 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 80/TCP,443/TCP,15443/TCP 7m43s
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>istio-ingressgateway LoadBalancer 10.111.24.207 10.111.24.207 15021:30945/TCP,80:30687/TCP,443:30520/TCP,31400:30072/TCP,15443:32717/TCP 7m43s
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>istiod ClusterIP 10.99.171.243 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 15010/TCP,15012/TCP,443/TCP,15014/TCP 7m58s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>→ 이 경우 10.111.24.207&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>predict 요청 날려보기&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl -X POST &amp;lt;http://10.111.24.207/seldon/seldon/iris-model/api/v1.0/predictions&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span> -H &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\\&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span> -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{ &amp;#34;data&amp;#34;: { &amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;: [[1,2,3,4]] } }&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>format
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>http://&amp;lt;ingress_url&amp;gt;/seldon/&amp;lt;namespace&amp;gt;/&amp;lt;model-name&amp;gt;/api/v1.0/doc/&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>다음과 같은 결과를 얻을 수 있습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;data&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;names&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;t:0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;t:1&amp;#34;&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;t:2&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[[&lt;/span>0.0006985194531162841,0.003668039039435755,0.9956334415074478&lt;span class="o">]]}&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;meta&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;requestPath&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;classifier&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;seldonio/sklearnserver:1.7.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="seldon-analytics">Seldon-analytics&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="install">Install&lt;/h3>
